Some people have problems downloading this torrent special utorrent users.
Go to Options / preferences / Advanced / Disk Cache

Overrride cache size: Disable
Reduce mem: Enable
Enable caching of disk writes: Disable
Enable caching of disk read: Disable
Disable windows caching of disk writes: Enable
Disable windows caching of disk reads: Enable

Works for lot of people fine after this setting, good luck.
